---

<section class="pres-risk">
  <div class="pres-risk__container">
    <div class="pres-risk__intro">
      <p class="pres-risk__eyebrow">The risk no one talks about</p>
      <h2 class="pres-risk__heading">The real risk is staying still.</h2>
      <p class="pres-risk__body">
        CD rates have already started to drop. Inflation does not pause while you decide. Every
        month sitting in a 4% account is a month not compounding at 8 to 10%. Doing nothing is not
        neutral. It is a position, and right now it is a losing one.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pres-risk__cards">
      <div class="pres-risk__card">
        <span class="pres-risk__card-label">CDs reset lower</span>
        <p class="pres-risk__card-body">
          Top yields have come down from 5.5% to roughly 4% in 18 months and are heading further
          south.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="pres-risk__card">
        <span class="pres-risk__card-label">Inflation keeps working</span>
        <p class="pres-risk__card-body">
          A 4% yield after taxes barely keeps pace with the cost of living.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="pres-risk__card">
        <span class="pres-risk__card-label">Time is the multiplier</span>
        <p class="pres-risk__card-body">
          Six months waiting at 4% vs 10% on $100k is roughly $3,000 you do not get back.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="pres-risk__source">For illustrative purposes only.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pres-risk {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-risk__container {
    max-width: 1024px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 72px 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .pres-risk__intro {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .pres-risk__eyebrow {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--green-dark);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 130%;
  }

  .pres-risk__heading {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    line-height: 115%;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-risk__body {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 165%;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-risk__cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .pres-risk__card {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .pres-risk__card-label {
    font-family: "Roboto Serif", serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    line-height: 130%;
  }

  .pres-risk__card-body {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 160%;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .pres-risk__source {
    font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 150%;
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 600px) {
    .pres-risk__container {
      padding: 96px 32px;
      gap: 48px;
    }

    .pres-risk__heading {
      font-size: 44px;
    }

    .pres-risk__cards {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media only screen and (min-width: 1136px) {
    .pres-risk__container {
      padding: 120px 48px;
    }
  }
</style>
